OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FThree out of five respondents who
OL,8,Fsuffer from headlight glare say the
OL,9,Fproblem has worsened in the previous
OL,10,F12 months, with only 26% disagreeing
OL,12,FA quarter (25%) of drivers who find
OL,13,Fvehicle headlights too bright are
OL,14,Fdriving less at night because of the
OL,15,Fissue, a new survey suggests.
OL,17,FThe poll of 1,866 drivers,
OL,18,Fcommissioned by the car insurance
OL,19,Fcompany RAC in December 2024,
OL,20,Findicated that 22% of participants
OL,21,Ftried to reduce their night driving.
