OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FNearly all drivers surveyed believe
OL,8,Fheadlights can be too bright, and 61%
OL,9,Fof those affected by glare say the
OL,10,Fproblem has become worse in the past
OL,11,Fyear, while 26% disagree.
OL,13,FThe survey also found that drivers
OL,14,Funder 35 (41%) are more likely to say
OL,15,Fheadlights are too bright, as are 38%
OL,16,Fof those who drive hatchbacks,
OL,17,Festates, or saloons, which sit lower
OL,18,Fon the road than SUVs.
