OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FA DfT spokesperson said: "We know
OL,8,Fthere is increased public concern
OL,9,Fabout headlamp glare ` that's why we
OL,10,Fhave commissioned independent research
OL,11,Fto better understand the root causes,
OL,12,Fwhich will help identify potential
OL,13,Fmitigations.
OL,15,F"This project is expected to conclude
OL,16,Fin the summer, and we will update on
OL,17,Fits findings as soon as possible."
