OL,7,FRAC senior policy officer Rod Dennis
OL,8,Fsaid: "With the exception of potholes,
OL,9,Ffew motoring topics seem to rouse as
OL,10,Fmuch interest among the nation's
OL,11,Fdrivers right now as bright headlights.
OL,13,F"What has gone from a mere frustration
OL,14,Fis now having a profound impact on
OL,15,Fpeople ` whether that's momentarily
OL,16,Fbeing blinded while driving or
OL,17,Fstruggling to judge the speed or
OL,18,Fposition of a vehicle ahead.
