OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FThe RAC says modern car headlights
OL,8,Fappear brighter due to the use of bi-
OL,9,Fxenon and LED bulbs, creating a more
OL,10,Fintense beam than traditional halogen
OL,11,Flights.
OL,13,FWhile this improves visibility for
OL,14,Fdrivers, it can make the road harder
OL,15,Fto see for others.
OL,17,FOther potential factors include badly
OL,18,Faligned headlights and the prevalence
OL,19,Fof SUVs, which generally have
OL,20,Fheadlights in a higher position.
